<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Bulk Availability Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .info {
            background-color: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .summary {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Bulk Availability Update</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Your availability has been updated in bulk for multiple time slots.</p>
        
        <div class="summary">
            <h3>Update Summary</h3>
            <p><strong>Date Range:</strong> {{startDate}} to {{endDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Days Affected:</strong> {{affectedDays}}</p>
            <p><strong>Total Slots:</strong> {{totalSlots}}</p>
            {{#if pattern}}
            <p><strong>Recurring Pattern:</strong> {{pattern}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="info">
            <p>These changes are now reflected in your calendar and visible to your clients.</p>
            <p>You can review and modify these slots individually through your provider dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Thank you for keeping your availability up to date!</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Eventide. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
